gs VOL.13 - Sidewalks (Vertex Paintable Debris/Water/Damage/Dirt)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes a detailed modular sidewalk kit with vertex‑paintable debris, water puddles, damage, and dirt overlays. Both Nanite‑optimized and low‑poly materials are provided—complete with master material controls and 4 K PBR textures. Ideal for urban scenes, streetscapes, or environmental storytelling. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/71be371c-905b-4c67-8ba9-9a876d23ab02" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildings_vol15_attachments"&gt;&lt;a id="buildings_vol15_attachments"&gt;Buildings VOL.15 - Attachments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c7c6611004e7a6fcfbd267fc4e993caa30ffff1c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=437b7af93a73857eedb168da3afaeb38"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Buildings VOL.15 - Attachments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A comprehensive collection of modular &lt;strong&gt;attachments&lt;/strong&gt; for buildings—such as awnings, signs, mailboxes, utility boxes, and pipes. Includes both Nanite-optimized and low-poly variants with detailed 4K PBR textures and master material options. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/349b1fe8-7481-4ef0-b629-568a40a9adda" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildings_vol16_flowerbeds"&gt;&lt;a id="buildings_vol16_flowerbeds"&gt;Buildings VOL.16 - Flower Beds&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/171848e4d9791f1f5d26085dc8c430111766b61e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3456c637344e0404d2b5d3e130437b13"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Buildings VOL.16 – Flower Beds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A vibrant modular &lt;strong&gt;Flower Beds&lt;/strong&gt; kit featuring raised planters, decorative pots, various flowers, shrubs, and exposed soil components. Includes both Nanite‑optimized and low‑poly versions with 4K PBR textures and master material controls—perfect for enhancing gardens, parks, or streetscapes. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/ea5cad22-a53e-41bc-a5f0-2169ecfdc2af" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="decals_vol1_townsigns"&gt;&lt;a id="decals_vol1_townsigns"&gt;Decals VOL.1 - Town Signs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6956b2fc3a79e9545a64fe2c98a1f7a39f019720.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9094c36a2489c1441b4ed7e6fead92ac"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Decals VOL.1 – Town Signs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A versatile collection of &lt;strong&gt;town sign decals&lt;/strong&gt;, including street names, directional signs, warning signs, and graffiti-covered signposts. Includes transparent PNGs and Unreal-ready materials for easy placement. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/2dbb5b0a-4e57-4734-a0fd-f1094e50b43c" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="decals_vol2_roadsandstreets"&gt;&lt;a id="decals_vol2_roadsandstreets"&gt;Decals VOL.2 - Roads and Streets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/19627a734f51a75012ae9062d85c9637a390fbca.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=101beed42d011230594f544b6fba6d06"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Decals VOL.2 – Roads and Streets&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A curated set of &lt;strong&gt;road and street decals&lt;/strong&gt;, including lane markings, crosswalks, manholes, cracks, and patched asphalt textures. Perfect for urban and roadway environment detailing in Unreal Engine. &lt;a href="https://www.fab.com/listings/bdb80537-d2dd-42d1-be36-63f3e8bdcde4" target="_blank"&gt;View on Fab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="decals_vol3_blood"&gt;&lt;a id="decals_vol3_blood"&gt;Decals VOL.3 - Blood&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f04a7dd12e7cbc2f61f5a77fd8d2faa51bc3007f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600