, packed with 221 all-new, royalty-free sound effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This volume includes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 18 Arcade Sounds: SFX from air hockey, bowling, and dodgeball for fast-paced, arcade-style gameplay.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 22 Fitness Sounds: Exercise machines, gym bags, and spring boxes—perfect for training montages and sports sims.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 39 Garden Game Sounds: Mini golf, horseshoes, and other outdoor leisure sounds that add a friendly, casual tone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 49 House Sport Sounds: Nerf battles and table tennis with detailed impact, bounce, and hit sounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 9 Misc Sounds: Unique additions like board waxing and hula hoops to round out any sporty soundscape.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 41 Pub Game Sounds: Darts and pool with satisfying chalks, throws, and cue impacts for bar-style minigames.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- 42 Wheel-Based Sport Sounds: Roller skating and skateboarding with starts, stops, tricks, and fast passes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you’re creating a stylized sports title or adding personality to recreational moments, this pack offers everything you need to score big.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz/16bit &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is loaded with metadata tags to reduce time searching for sounds.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bugssoundfxpack_vol2"&gt;&lt;a id="bugssoundfxpack_vol2" href="https://youtu.be/-vluB8M2SkA"&gt;Bugs Sound FX Pack Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3822db6e5c4abd2e36c0fb1c18ee6eb672596d66.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ae30f1f01103730228a1486597381aeb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Returning with Volume 2 of the Microscale: Bugs Sound FX Pack by Ovani Sound – an intricate collection of small-scale insect sounds designed to bring realism, texture, and detail to your tiniest creatures and scenes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 238 total sounds, this pack delivers richly layered audio that captures the subtle yet dynamic world of bugs and crawlers. Ideal for fantasy, nature sims, sci-fi swarms, or stylized platformers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 20 Chitter Chatter Sounds – Fast clicks, scratchy vocalizations, and distinctive bug chatter.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 11 Ant Sounds – Footsteps and hard-surface scurries from precision-paced insects.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 29 Carapice and Exoskeleton Sounds – Shell crackles, chitin shifts, and armored movement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Crawl and Flurry Sounds – Multi-limbed motion, frantic bursts, and scuttling textures.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 19 Eat Sounds – Tiny crunches, single bites, and layered chewing sequences.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 22 Forage Sounds – Small rustles, leaf disturbances, and rummaging dirt scrapes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 41 Leap and Land Sounds – Jumps, wing flaps, and grassy landings for bugs of all sizes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 17 Mandibles Sounds – Sharp snaps, pinches, and probing insect mouthparts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 20 Misc Sounds – Plant interactions, bioluminescent flicks, and environmental oddities.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 12 Molting Sounds – Squelches and rustles of bugs shedding and transforming.&lt;p&gt;Every sound in this pack is brand new and exclusive to Volume 2 – no recycled material. Created from layered source recordings, these files bring tiny performances to life for projects that focus on detail and immersion.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each file is tagged with detailed metadata for fast implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="wildwestsoundfxpack"&gt;&lt;a id="wildwestsoundfxpack" href="https://youtu.be/RkKqIp31fgU"&gt;Wild West Sound FX Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/800bfd9d539846cf1078ae3158877a039e1804f5.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7fd6201b191d8ee5e8fae0c90346ce56"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Introducing the Wild West Sound FX Pack Vol. 1 by Ovani Sound – a rootin’ tootin’ collection of western-inspired audio built for saloon scuffles, dusty duels, and tales of frontier grit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With 220 total sounds, this pack brings rugged charm and cinematic flavor to wild west adventures, cowboy-themed games, and Americana settings:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• 9 Communications Sounds: Distinct morse code signals for scripted moments and callouts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 21 Foley Sounds: Spur-clinking footsteps, shoveling grit, and rugged apparel movements.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 43 Instrumentation Sounds: Slide guitars, harmonicas, tremolos, and twangy stingers for dramatic transitions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 16 Outlaws Sounds: Duel whistles, bounty slaps, and lawless audio cues.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 62 Saloon Sounds: Dice rolls, card flips, chips clinking, swinging doors, and spittoon pings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 14 Voices: Yells, yee-haws, and character lines for outlaw NPCs or rowdy townies.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 55 Weapons Sounds: Pistols, lassos, whips, dynamite, and blade sharpening for tense stand-offs.&lt;p&gt;Each sound was recorded and designed to evoke classic western film aesthetics while offering clean utility for games, film, and interactive media.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;44.1kHz / 16bit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;All files come with embedded metadata for fast search and smooth implementation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="ambientmusicpack_vol10"&gt;&lt;a id="ambientmusicpack_vol10"&gt;Ambient Music Pack Vol. 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/25fc502e5cf43e3a6cf56f97062c75e4ac92d809.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7cf41e08ae4c3c877e267cdb4b423717"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;iframe width="100%" height="450" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/playlists/2048201274%3Fsecret_token%3Ds-5loyep0rVV2&amp;amp;color=%23ff5500&amp;amp;auto_play=false&amp;amp;hide_related=false&amp;amp;show_comme