ions in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython"&gt;Intro to Object-Oriented Programming with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pythonprojects_object-orientedgame"&gt;Python Projects - Object-Oriented Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoalgorithmswithpython"&gt;Intro to Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildawebapplicationwithflask"&gt;Build a Web Application with Flask&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment"&gt;Intro to Flask for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#graphsdatastructureandalgorithmswithpython"&gt;Graphs Data Structure and Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame"&gt;JavaScript Mini-Projects - Language Learning Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable"&gt;Intermediate JavaScript - Build a Dynamic Data Table&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completeintroductiontocplusplus"&gt;The Complete Introduction to C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtocplusplusdatastructures"&gt;Intro to C++ Data Structures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame"&gt;Learn Object-Oriented C++ by Building a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming"&gt;The Comprehensive Introduction to C# Programming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aipromptengineeringforprogrammers"&gt;Prompt Engineering for Programmers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#intermediatepython_learnpygamebymakingagame"&gt;Intermediate Python - Learn Pygame by Making a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#introtouianduxdesign"&gt;Intro to UI/UX Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#javascriptprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;JavaScript Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bta1"&gt;Pay more than the average of $23.99 to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/eTpmZnklWJk"&gt;JavaScript Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn JavaScript - one of the core pillars of both web and HTML5 game development.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;JavaScript is a high-level language that powers much of the world wide web - from some of the most popular frameworks and libraries to browser-based games, mobile games, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Through this course, you will master the fundamentals of the language in ways that can be adapted for both web and game development, and learn essential skills that will help you to expand and create your own JavaScript-based projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up and run JavaScript code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use variables, operators, and arrays for data management&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control program flow with loops and conditionals&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create functions to perform specific tasks&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize JavaScript objects to store datasets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement interactivity with event handling&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="htmlfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="htmlfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/pV1gB5DXGCI"&gt;HTML Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build websites, web apps, and more by learning the primary foundation for all web development - HTML.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML (Hypertext Markup Language) is the core pillar of web development that dictates the structure and base appearance of every webpage, and plays a crucial role as you develop your skills further with CSS and JavaScript.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this course, you will develop a strong set of HTML skills needed to get started on your web development journey, as you learn to structure your page, add specific elements, and even start adding website interactivity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create your first HTML file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle text and its various attributes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Utilize images, links, lists, tables, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with classes and IDs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Display HTML elements in various ways&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Deal with various user inputs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="cssfoundations"&gt;&lt;a id="cssfoundations" href="https://youtu.be/qrVxf6SNvgc"&gt;CSS Foundations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master website aesthetics and responsiveness by learning the fundamentals of CSS - a core pillar of web development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cascading Style Sheets, otherwise known as CSS, is a language geared at altering the appearance of HTML and other markup languages - from page aesthetics, like colors and fonts, to designs that respond to screen size.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course will get you started with the basics of this powerful style sheet language and provide you an in-demand set of skills to enhance the design of your personal and professional web development projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Import CSS into your web project&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Select various HTML elements to alter&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Position and size elements with CSS&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; colors and various stylings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Alter margins and padding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adjust backgrounds, borders, text, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtowebdevelopmentwithhtmlandcss"&gt;&lt;a id="introtowebdevelopmentwithhtmlandcss" href="https://youtu.be/qoYtK7yoM54"&gt;Intro to Web Development with HTML and CSS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;HTML and CSS are the core pillars of web development - they form the foundations upon which every website is built.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Used to create web pages, web apps, and HTML5 games, these in-demand, highly popular languages are also easy to learn - making them great starting points for those with no prior coding experience.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn HTML and CSS, and master how to work with text, links, images, forms, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create headlines, paragraphs, and lists&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add images, links, forms, and tables&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with IDs and classes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply different fonts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change spacings and alignments&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="createyourfirstresponsivewebsite"&gt;&lt;a id="createyourfirstresponsivewebsite" href="https://youtu.be/bJN0uDEuymc"&gt;Create Your First Responsive Website&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover how to build your first responsive website using only basic HTML and CSS!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You'll learn by creating a company-style website featuring navigation, a banner, and grid-displayed services, and master techniques for automatically altering its appearance based on screen size.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Lay out various webpage sections with HTML&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use Chrome Developer Tools&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create a navigation bar with hover effects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Display widescreen images for a splash banner&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Showcase elements in a grid-style format&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up CSS rules for different screen sizes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="build3dwebappswithbabylonjs"&gt;&lt;a id="build3dwebappswithbabylonjs" href="https://youtu.be/aeoDVO789wE"&gt;Build 3D Web Apps with Babylon.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bring 3D graphics to the web by mastering Babylon.js - a real-time, 3D render engine for HTML5 websites.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Based on WebGL, Babylon.js allows you to render static and animated 3D scenes using the HTML Canvas. Through this course, you'll explore the foundations of using Babylon.js for your projects by building a simple solar system scene. Whether you want to create dynamic web-UIs, eye-catching showcases, or build an interactive scene, you will gain all the skills needed to build your 3D project right in your browser!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up and test Babylon.js scenes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement simple and complex 3D objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate 3D objects scaling, rotation, and position&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize materials to change object appearance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Adjust cameras and lighting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Animate 3D objects using only code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtosqlanddatabaseswithmysql"&gt;&lt;a id="introtosqlanddatabaseswithmysql" href="https://youtu.be/ug6DR87bbfk"&gt;Intro to SQL and Databases with MySQL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the essential skills to manage and query databases using SQL!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Structured Query Language (SQL) is the backbone of modern databases, enabling developers to store, retrieve, and manipulate data efficiently. In this course, you'll gain a solid foundation in relational databases and work with MySQL to explore real-world techniques like filtering data, combining tables, and more. By mastering these skills, you'll unlock the ability to manage data systems for applications, websites, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Retrieve data with SELECT queries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Filter, group, and aggregate data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add new data with various techniques&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine data with SQL JOIN operations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with UPDATE and DELETE&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maintain data integrity in databases&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnrustprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="learnrustprogrammingforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/__Fjvbcx_vg"&gt;Learn Rust Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dive into the fundamentals of Rust and unlock unparalleled efficiency!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Rust is a general-purpose programming language that’s revolutionizing software development with its emphasis on performance and type-safe coding standards. In this course, you'll journey through Rust's unique features, exploring why developers are increasingly leaning towards it for building real-world applications. By mastering these skills with Rust, you will be equipped to tackle high-performance projects in sectors like web development, systems programming, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up your Rust environment&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand basic Rust syntax&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize Rust's ownership system&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement control flow in Rust&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create and use structs and enums&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Leverage crates and modules for efficiency&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="datastructureswithrust"&gt;&lt;a id="datastructureswithrust" href="https://youtu.be/kmvy2qqKVkk"&gt;Data Structures with Rust&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of data structures with Rust!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Data structures are the backbone of efficient coding, and mastering them can make the difference between elegant solutions and cumbersome code. In this course, you'll delve into the world of Rust, applying and implementing essential data structures from start to finish. These Rust skills will allow you to select the ideal structure for any situation, streamlining your coding efficiency and preparing you for real-world applications.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Familiarity with programming principles and Rust is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize Rust's Vectors effectively&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with HashMaps efficiently&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement stacks from scratch&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create queues independently&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle errors with options&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use Rust for safe data management&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rustparallelcomputingproject_imageprocessor"&gt;&lt;a id="rustparallelcomputingproject_imageprocessor" href="https://youtu.be/3ubPa6c6emY"&gt;Rust Parallel Computing Project - Image Processor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of image processing for Rust applications!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Rust's Image Crate (or library) offers developers a quick and easy way to perform common image manipulations on files - a much-needed skill in today's media-driven world. In this course, you'll learn how to programmatically edit images while also exploring Rust's parallel computing abilities to improve program efficiency. These skills will not only give you greater control over image-based features, but allow you to start using concurrent execution for any Rust-made project.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Familiarity with programming principles and Rust is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Resize images&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rotate images&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Crop images&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Blur images&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with image ratios&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process images in bulk&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="practicalrust_clitoolswithclapandindicatif"&gt;&lt;a id="practicalrust_clitoolswithclapandindicatif" href="https://youtu.be/ZxZYsHTttJ4"&gt;Practical Rust - CLI Tools with Clap and Indicatif&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elevate your Rust skills by building a dynamic CLI application!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In today's fast-paced development world, command-line interfaces (CLIs) are vital for creating efficient and user-friendly applications. In this course, you'll transform a basic image-processing app into a fully-fledged Rust-powered CLI tool. Mastering these skills expands your ability to develop real-world, efficient programs that deliver results using the powerful Rust language.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;An intermediate understanding of Rust, parallel computing, and image processing is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Parse command-line arguments&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle complex subcommand&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add progress bars with Indicatif&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Improve user interaction dynamically&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Execute tasks with CLI efficiency&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create versatile Rust applications&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rustwebappproject_collaborativedocumentediting"&gt;&lt;a id="rustwebappproject_collaborativedocumentediting" href="https://youtu.be/AbhnFkO-Qa8"&gt;Rust Web App Project - Collaborative Document Editing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build a real-world collaborative document editing web application using Rust!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In a digital age where collaboration is key, mastering the technologies behind real-time document editing can set you apart. Through this course, you'll dive deep into creating a fully-fledged web app that supports simultaneous document editing with Rust's web framework Actix Web and WebSockets - and seamlessly integrate them with JavaScript. These skills will empower you to explore Rust web development and provide you with a stunning portfolio piece.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up Rust web projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Configure and manage dependencies&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand WebSockets fundamentals&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Develop WebSocket endpoints in Rust&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Synchronize real-time data efficiently&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate JavaScript for the front-end&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rustwebappproject_real-timevideobroadcasting"&gt;&lt;a id="rustwebappproject_real-timevideobroadcasting" href="https://youtu.be/V8IRPJJldec"&gt;Rust Web App Project - Real-Time Video Broadcasting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master real-time video broadcasting with Rust!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Real-time communication is revolutionizing how we interact online, affecting fields from gaming to remote work. Through this course, you'll create a simple video broadcasting system using Rust, WebRTC, and JavaScript - gaining deep insights into real-time communication protocols. These cutting-edge skills will empower you to build fully-fledged applications for live streaming and beyond.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;An intermediate understanding of Rust, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Utilize WebRTC for video streaming&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Establish peer-to-peer connections&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Integrate Rust with JavaScript&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Configure ICE servers effectively&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply Session Description Protocol (SDP)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Streamline client-side experiences&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtodevelopingaiagentswithpythonandcrewai"&gt;&lt;a id="introtodevelopingaiagentswithpythonandcrewai" href="https://youtu.be/T74czwa3PXc"&gt;Intro to Developing AI Agents with Python &amp; CrewAI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master multi-agent AI and create intelligent applications!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the world of AI, multi-agent systems are a groundbreaking approach where intelligent agents work together to solve complex tasks. Through this course, you'll unlock the power of CrewAI – a robust framework for building collaborative AI systems – by exploring real-world projects where agents communicate, share knowledge, and collaborate on research tasks seamlessly. These skills will allow you to create increasingly complex AI solutions and optimize workflows efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up and configure CrewAI projects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create and customize multi-agent systems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integrate cloud-based and local LLMs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Define and execute agent-specific tasks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Optimize agents for long-running operations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Develop custom AI tools for unique needs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aiagentprojectwithpythonandcrewai"&gt;&lt;a id="aiagentprojectwithpythonandcrewai" href="https://youtu.be/3l1AhJLiO3M"&gt;AI Agent Project with Python &amp; CrewAI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create an AI-powered study assistant with Python and CrewAI!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;AI-powered applications are revolutionizing productivity and education, making learning smarter and more personalized. In this course, you’ll develop a complete Study Buddy app using the CrewAI framework that processes PDFs, generates concise summaries, and creates quizzes and flashcards to reinforce knowledge. With these skills, you’ll understand how to build advanced multi-agent AI systems and gain the expertise to design similar real-world applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up an AI-driven agent app&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage multi-agent tasks seamlessly&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Process text with OpenAI’s API&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Integrate local large language models&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create terminal-based flashcard commands&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Generate quizzes from summarized content&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtodjangoforpythonwebappdevelopment2025edition"&gt;&lt;a id="introtodjangoforpythonwebappdevelopment2025edition" href="https://youtu.be/Wqb_c3eDu-Q"&gt;Intro to Django for Python Web App Development (2025 Edition)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to build dynamic web apps with Django, the powerful Python-based framework!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Django is a high-level, open-source framework that simplifies the creation of dynamic and scalable web applications. In this course, you'll build a fully-fledged multi-page website, exploring key concepts such as Django's Model-View-Template (MVT) architecture, dynamic content generation, and project organization. By the end, you'll have the foundational skills needed to create your own complete web app projects and expand into more Django topics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up and configure a Django project&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Understand Django's MVT architecture&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create dynamic templates with context data&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control page navigation with URLs and views&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Work with static files, including CSS&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build a simple multi-page web app&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnvibecodingwithcursor"&gt;&lt;a id="learnvibecodingwithcursor" href="https://youtu.be/jNKvCF6RxtE"&gt;Learn Vibe Coding with Cursor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock productivity with vibe coding and AI-driven development using Cursor.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vibe coding is transforming how projects get made: simply share your ideas and let AI handle the technical details - so you can build more, faster. In this course, you’ll immerse yourself in the vibe coding approach as you use Cursor to create a complete, real-world Flask image resizer from start to finish. With practical exercises and step-by-step guidance, you’ll discover how Cursor and vibe coding supercharges your workflow, letting you focus on creativity and results.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You’ll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Adopt the vibe coding mindset&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Boost productivity with Cursor’s features&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Write powerful, effective AI prompts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build a Flask image resizer app&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Test, secure, and expand your code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply vibe coding to any project&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtocodingwithpythonturtle2025edition"&gt;&lt;a id="introtocodingwithpythonturtle2025edition" href="https://youtu.be/RthzRcnxcSk"&gt;Intro to Coding with Python Turtle (2025 Edition)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Visualize code and master Python basics with Turtle!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Grasping core programming concepts is easier when you can see your code come to life. In this course, you'll explore coding fundamentals using the engaging Python Turtle graphics library, creating algorithms you can see and building a complete project visualizing our solar system. These foundational Python skills will empower you to tackle more complex programming challenges, master other integral coding principles, and discover how to build algorithms from scratch!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master fundamental Python syntax&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand core algorithm concepts&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Draw shapes using Turtle&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply colors and fills&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Visualize algorithms on screen&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build a visual solar system with code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonturtlemini-projects2025edition"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonturtlemini-projects2025edition" href="https://youtu.be/J0iY3qOT-s0"&gt;Python Turtle Mini-Projects (2025 Edition)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your Python skills with engaging Turtle projects!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Python Turtle provides a fun, visual way to bring your code to life and create unique and interactive projects with ease. Through this course, you'll build three distinct graphical mini-projects from start to finish, while learning essential Python concepts like variables, loops, and functions. These practical skills will solidify your understanding of programming fundamentals, preparing you to tackle more complex Python applications for the real world.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with data, variables, and operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement conditional logic&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimize code with functions and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use randomization&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle user keyboard input&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure complete mini-projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythondatastructuresforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="pythondatastructuresforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/7fh-e5Atz8U"&gt;Python Data Structures for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn fundamental data structures for Python programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Data structures are a tool that allows us to store multiple data values efficiently and maintain specific relationships between those stored values. In this course, you'll explore some of the core Python data structures available, their use cases, and how to practically apply these uses to a text-based RPG battle. These skills will not only give you a foundational element of programming but provide you new methods to organize and manage your program data.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store multiple values as lists&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control strings as sequences of data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with key-value pairs in dictionaries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use tuples and sets based on scenario&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate all data structures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply data structures to games&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pandasproject_flightdataanalysis"&gt;&lt;a id="pandasproject_flightdataanalysis" href="https://youtu.be/wnOINkMZfus"&gt;Pandas Project - Flight Data Analysis&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master Pandas data analysis using real-world flight data!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Data analysis and visualization are critical for almost every industry in making data-backed decisions. Through this course, you'll use Pandas to explore real-world flight data and learn methods for grouping, filtering, and visualizing data in ways applicable to real life. These techniques will unlock new ways you can leverage your data for insights and provide core skills for the entirety of data science.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Basic familiarity with Python, NumPy, and Pandas is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Load external spreadsheet data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Explore data structures for analysis&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Filter data for various criteria&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Group data for different analyses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create different chart types&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Leverage the above for data insights&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonimageprocessingwithpillow"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonimageprocessingwithpillow" href="https://youtu.be/ZYHYB0_W1f8"&gt;Python Image Processing with Pillow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to work with images in Python using Pillow!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Pillow, a fork of the Python Imaging Library (PIL), is a popular tool for manipulating and saving digital images through easy-to-use modules. Through this course, you'll explore basic image operations with Pillow and learn to apply rotation, color changes, filters, and much more. These techniques will allow you to unlock the power of images for your Python apps and give you efficient ways to alter those images to your needs.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A basic understanding of Python is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Display and save images&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change rotations and image dimensions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Alter image color values&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Enhance contrast, brightness, and more&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use common filters like blurring&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add aspects like borders&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="intermediatepython_virtualpetwithpygame"&gt;&lt;a id="intermediatepython_virtualpetwithpygame" href="https://youtu.be/XzEDiXdG-lk"&gt;Intermediate Python - Virtual Pet with Pygame&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Craft a virtual pet game with Python and Pygame!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Virtual pets are a popular stress-relief genre that allow players to engage with risk-free pet care. You'll work with the Pygame library and create a simple pet game with basic care options and needs system for the pet. These techniques will both enhance your skills with Python and give you new tools to create fun or educational games to play.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Basic skills with Python are needed to take this course. Pygame skills are also helpful, but optional.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use project management techniques&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create item and pet objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control mouse click interactions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement movement and collisions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add "decay" to pet needs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up end game criteria&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoregularexpressionsinpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoregularexpressionsinpython" href="https://youtu.be/PkTsr1kniDk"&gt;Intro to Regular Expressions in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock new data management techniques in Python with regular expressions!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Regular expressions (RegEx) are a dynamic syntax of characters that provide easy ways to parse, clean, and extract data from text. In this course, you'll explore the foundations of regular expressions and learn a variety of sequences and characters to search your data dynamically. These skills will allow you to apply algorithms to complex data and more quickly find the data you need for your projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Basic familiarity with Python is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create basic patterns using metacharacters&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Refine extracted characters with classes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Anchor searches from specific points&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define character quantity to extract&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Group patterns for complex searches&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply techniques to real-life projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoobject-orientedprogrammingwithpython" href="https://youtu.be/D-mB0rqXFsI"&gt;Intro to Object-Oriented Programming with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;With applications in data science, computer vision, and machine learning, Python has been used to automate tasks, create AAA games and effects for blockbuster films, and build cutting-edge technologies like smart cars and facial recognition systems.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of Python - including techniques for working with data, program logic, and more. The skills that you'll learn can be applied to building games, apps, and more, and can form the foundations of more advanced programs.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store simple data values with variables&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Save sets of data with lists, tuples, and dictionaries&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control logic flow with conditionals and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up program logic with functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with classes and objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pythonprojects_object-orientedgame"&gt;&lt;a id="pythonprojects_object-orientedgame" href="https://youtu.be/sWtQe8a-HuU"&gt;Python Projects - Object-Oriented Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master object-oriented programming techniques for games using Python!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Object-oriented programming (OOP) is one of the most in-demand paradigms, offering developers efficient and intuitive ways to organize their code. In this course, you'll use the Python language to create a text-based escape room while exploring core techniques for working with game "objects" and object-oriented principles. These OOP foundations will prepare you to pursue any number of interactive projects with responsible habits, whether it's games or other software projects!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage game projects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement different interaction types&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure. store, &amp;amp; display item data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Evaluate inputs for specific answers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Test your games for errors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Consider various impacts games have&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoalgorithmswithpython"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoalgorithmswithpython" href="https://youtu.be/FWGbmk3Abnw"&gt;Intro to Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn fundamental algorithms for searching and sorting data!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Computer science has many long-standing core algorithms to accomplish specific tasks quickly and efficiently. In this Python course, you'll examine a small sampling of algorithms used every day for searching and sorting data - and discover the pros and cons of each method. These skills will provide you new tools to approach data and give you the foundations needed to scale your projects for large amounts of data.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A basic understanding of Python and data structures is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn all about:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;What algorithms are&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Linear searches&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Binary searches&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Bubble sorting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Insertion sorting&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Comparing algorithm efficiency&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildawebapplicationwithflask"&gt;&lt;a id="buildawebapplicationwithflask" href="https://youtu.be/8-pzWxPF4IA"&gt;Build a Web Application with Flask&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Make a recipe posting and sharing web app with Flask!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;User interaction has become a core feature of the web app ecosystem, and Flask makes implementing these features easy. In this course, you'll master how to work with routes, forms, and user authentication in Flask while building a site where users can post and share recipes. These skills will allow you to expand your web app skills with Flask and implement user activity for your web app projects.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A solid understanding of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python, and Flask&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create intermediate database models&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Work with forms in Flask&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up user registration&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control authorized page access&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Implement user-sharing features&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build website navigation integrating routes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="introtoflaskforwebappdevelopment" href="https://youtu.be/BO9aygF8ta0"&gt;Intro to Flask for Web App Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore web app development with Flask!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Popularized by its simplicity and flexibility, Flask is a micro web framework that allows you to build web applications using Python. In this course, you'll explore the fundamentals of how Flask works while setting up a dynamic to-do list application - complete with database functionality. These skills will provide you the stepping stones necessary to develop more robust apps with Flask and unlock Python for the web.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Basic knowledge of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python are needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up a Flask project&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create dynamic web routes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage pages with templates&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Add database CRUD functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Restructure apps modularly&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use Flask's built-in debugging&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="graphsdatastructureandalgorithmswithpython"&gt;&lt;a id="graphsdatastructureandalgorithmswithpython" href="https://youtu.be/-kkpimIyBRA"&gt;Graphs Data Structure and Algorithms with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the graph data structure for enhanced relationship mapping!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Graphs are a robust data structure that allow you to link "nodes" together with edges to show connections and paths between elements. Through this course, you'll construct methods to implement a graph structure - and also dive into search algorithms to make the most of the data. These skills will give you the means to map complex relationships in Python that are useful for real-world problems like transportation networks, social networks, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;A basic understanding of Python and data structures is needed for this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn all about:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Undirected graphs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Directed graphs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Weights&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Breadth First Search&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Depth First Search&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cycles in graphs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptmini-projects_languagelearninggame" href="https://youtu.be/9n97L2snd3w"&gt;JavaScript Mini-Projects - Language Learning Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your JavaScript skills by building a browser-based language learning app!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;With no additional frameworks or libraries required, you'll create a quiz-based game while learning how to dynamically integrate JavaScript into webpages, and mastering skills and systems that can be used to create a wide variety of apps and games.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Structure an app with multiple questions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Change the questions and answers the DOM displays&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Detect user input&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process correct and incorrect answers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Track and display scores&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Style the app's appearance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable"&gt;&lt;a id="intermediatejavascript_buildadynamicdatatable" href="https://youtu.be/xa8KLNRi_Hw"&gt;Intermediate JavaScript - Build a Dynamic Data Table&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expand your JavaScript skills by exploring the concepts of asynchronous programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Asynchronous programming is an important method of programming that allows certain tasks to be performed in parallel with the main task. In this course, you'll build a filterable trading card table while exploring how to utilize async functions in JavaScript to dynamically fetch and manipulate data in real-time from a separate JSON file. These concepts will give you the skills to build robust websites, work with API data, and more.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand promises and async functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Handle errors in async programming&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use fetch() to retrieve JSON data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Write clean code with arrow functions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Display retrieved data in a table&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Dynamically filter data on the DOM&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completeintroductiontocplusplus"&gt;&lt;a id="completeintroductiontocplusplus" href="https://youtu.be/-2jyQDsJiCY"&gt;The Complete Introduction to C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the foundations of C++ programming!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;C++ is the powerhouse behind many advanced tech - including web browsers, operating systems, games, and cloud platforms. Industry leaders like Microsoft, Google, and Apple use C++ to power the innovations that shape our world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of working with C++ as you explore techniques for storing and manipulating data - from controlling how your program executes to keeping your code clean.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Handle output and input&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Store various pieces of data with variables&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manipulate and evaluate data with operators&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manage flow with conditionals, loops, and more&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create reusable blocks of code&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up a local C++ development environment&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtocplusplusdatastructures"&gt;&lt;a id="introtocplusplusdatastructures" href="https://youtu.be/iXhH2fI-v_k"&gt;Intro to C++ Data Structures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enhance your knowledge of C++ by exploring data structures.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Knowing how to deal with data structures in C++ is an essential skill for all sorts of C++ programs. Through this course, you'll learn how to store different kinds of data and how you can manipulate and control these data structures in useful ways. These C++ foundations will help prepare you to handle complex data with actionable, problem-solving skills to suit a variety of programming situations.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store lists of similar data in a single variable&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create entities with multiple variable values&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Reference memory addresses with pointers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use pointers with operators, arrays, and structs&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define custom datatypes of limited values (enumerations)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rename datatypes with Typedef&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame"&gt;&lt;a id="learnobject-orientedcplusplusbybuildingagame" href="https://youtu.be/_XXdIgZJzrA"&gt;Learn Object-Oriented C++ by Building a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore object-oriented C++ programming!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Object-oriented programming is a popular paradigm where developers build their programs around "objects" that contain data and functionality related to that object. In this course, you'll explore how to create objects and classes and access their data - all while building a text-based dungeon crawler. This knowledge will provide you with one of the most important skill sets you'll need to create robust C++ programs or even pursue a professional programming career.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create basic classes and objects&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control how data in objects is accessed&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manage OOP principles such as inheritance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Build text-based dungeons with various rooms&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Deal with player and enemy movement&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Setup interaction systems for combat and items&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming"&gt;&lt;a id="comprehensiveintroductiontocprogramming" href="https://youtu.be/XIJ_JAR5FpM"&gt;The Comprehensive Introduction to C# Programming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jumpstart your programming journey with the C# language!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Developed by Microsoft, C# is a versatile and robust language powering everything from simple applications to complex software systems. In this course, you'll dive deep into C# and explore foundational programming topics - all while cementing your learning with real-world examples and exercises. By the end, you'll have the foundational knowledge to excel in web development, mobile app creation, and even game development using major frameworks like Unity and MonoGame.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You'll learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up a C# development environment&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand C# syntax and execution&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Process and manipulate data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store data - including with collections&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create efficient code with loops and methods&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply fundamentals to real-world examples&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="aipromptengineeringforprogrammers"&gt;&lt;a id="aipromptengineeringforprogrammers" href="https://youtu.be/WWGZFIKRmyg"&gt;Prompt Engineering for Programmers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Modernize your approach to development with AI!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;AI is vastly changing the tech industry with new and intuitive techniques for development. You'll explore how to apply AI to your coding projects and render prompts that help you code, debug, and learn programming - fast! These skills will give you amazing tools to boost your productivity and overall enhance how you code.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;With AI, you will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Prompt AI for different scenarios&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Generate code in different languages&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Clean &amp;amp; optimize current code&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Produce commit messages &amp;amp; documentation&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Get testing and debugging help&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Tune prompts for certain outcomes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="intermediatepython_learnpygamebymakingagame"&gt;&lt;a id="intermediatepython_learnpygamebymakingagame" href="https://youtu.be/7XoLJimxJos"&gt;Intermediate Python - Learn Pygame by Making a Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to program with Python and Pygame by building a game from scratch!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Python is one of the most in-demand languages, and with the addition of multimedia, you can also make games with it. Using Pygame, a set of Python modules designed specifically for game development, you'll explore a variety of fundamental game mechanics such as players, enemies, and more - all while creating a simple road-crossing game with each step. These skills will give you the tools needed to make real-world apps and games using Python no matter the project!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Implement basic game window functionality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Draw images to the screen&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create player and enemy object classes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Listen for key presses to control movement&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Detect collisions between objects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Control gameplay flow with winning and losing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="introtouianduxdesign"&gt;&lt;a id="introtouianduxdesign" href="https://youtu.be/hKe4ndz6ecg"&gt;Intro to UI/UX Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore the foundations of UI and UX design!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The user interface (UI) and user experience (UX) have critical impacts on the usability of your projects - and can make or break its user appeal. In this course, you'll learn design methodologies for developing a UI/UX for a movie rating app while exploring audience targeting, iterative design, and wireframing. These skills will enable you to fine-tune your UI-design process and apply purposeful decisions to get the most optimal UX!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;No experience is needed to dive into this course.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Define projects with user stories&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create UIs with wireframes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Communicate navigation via wireframing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Consider user viewpoints for UX&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Iterate designs via testing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Understand the full design process&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="javascriptprogrammingforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="javascriptprogrammingforbeginners" href="https://youtu.be/ADY7kWvhJo4"&gt;JavaScript Programming for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Considered a core pillar of web development and one of the world's most in-demand languages, JavaScript is used for everything from building websites to creating web apps, HTML5 games, mobile and Internet of Things (IoT) apps, and even space exploration technology.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;In this beginner-friendly course, you'll learn the basics of this lightweight, cross-platform scripting language, and master skills that allow you to add dynamic, interactive content to your websites and apps.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;strong&gt;You will learn how to:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Store data as variables and arrays&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Manipulate data with operators&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Use conditionals to evaluate data for specific actions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control program logic and flow with functions and loops&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set up objects to store complex sets of data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Alter webpages with the DOM API&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;... and more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bta1"&gt;Pay more than the average of $23.99 to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
